---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="fr"
  title="Guides Fitness &amp; Musculation - AIVancePro"
  description="Guides complets de fitness et musculation. Apprenez les bases, cr&eacute;ez votre programme et progressez efficacement."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/guides/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/guides/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/guides/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/ratgeber/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .page-header {
        padding: 9rem 2rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gray-50), var(--white));
      }
      .section-label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--blue);
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      .page-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .page-header p {
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        max-width: 550px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .guides-grid {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      .guide-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--gray-900);
        transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .guide-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .guide-card .card-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 180px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-100), var(--gray-200));
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .guide-card .card-content {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .guide-card .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06);
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--blue);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        width: fit-content;
      }
      .guide-card h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }
      .guide-card p {
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        flex: 1;
      }
      .guide-card .meta {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .cta-section {
        padding: 5rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #1a1145);
        color: var(--white);
      }
      .cta-section h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .cta-section p {
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        font-size: 1rem;
        max-width: 450px;
        margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue), var(--purple));
        color: var(--white);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        opacity: 0.92;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .page-header { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
        .page-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        .guides-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="section-label">Guides</div>
    <h1>Guides complets</h1>
    <p>Des guides d&eacute;taill&eacute;s pour ma&icirc;triser chaque aspect de votre entra&icirc;nement, du d&eacute;butant &agrave; l'avanc&eacute;.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="guides-grid">
    <a href="/guides/debutant-musculation/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo Guide d&eacute;butant</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">D&eacute;butant</span>
        <h2>Guide du d&eacute;butant en musculation</h2>
        <p>Tout ce que vous devez savoir pour commencer la musculation : exercices de base, structure de programme et erreurs &agrave; &eacute;viter.</p>
        <div class="meta">15 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/creer-programme-entrainement/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo Programme</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Programmation</span>
        <h2>Cr&eacute;er un programme d'entra&icirc;nement efficace</h2>
        <p>S&eacute;ries, r&eacute;p&eacute;titions, fr&eacute;quence et volume : les cl&eacute;s pour construire un programme qui donne des r&eacute;sultats.</p>
        <div class="meta">12 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/nutrition-musculation/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo Nutrition</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Nutrition</span>
        <h2>Nutrition et musculation : le guide complet</h2>
        <p>Prot&eacute;ines, calories, macros et timing des repas. Tout comprendre pour optimiser vos r&eacute;sultats par l'alimentation.</p>
        <div class="meta">18 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/recuperation-prevention-blessures/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo R&eacute;cup&eacute;ration</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">R&eacute;cup&eacute;ration</span>
        <h2>R&eacute;cup&eacute;ration et pr&eacute;vention des blessures</h2>
        <p>Sommeil, stretching, deload et gestion de la fatigue. Apprenez &agrave; r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer pour mieux progresser.</p>
        <div class="meta">10 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/periodisation/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo P&eacute;riodisation</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Avanc&eacute;</span>
        <h2>Les bases de la p&eacute;riodisation</h2>
        <p>Microcycles, m&eacute;socycles et macrocycles : structurez votre entra&icirc;nement sur le long terme pour progresser sans stagner.</p>
        <div class="meta">14 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/progresser-developpe-couche/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo D&eacute;velopp&eacute; couch&eacute;</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Force</span>
        <h2>Comment progresser au d&eacute;velopp&eacute; couch&eacute;</h2>
        <p>Technique, programmation et exercices accessoires pour augmenter votre d&eacute;velopp&eacute; couch&eacute; efficacement.</p>
        <div class="meta">11 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/home-gym/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo Home Gym</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Home Gym</span>
        <h2>Guide du home gym : s'entra&icirc;ner chez soi</h2>
        <p>&Eacute;quipement essentiel, am&eacute;nagement et programmes adapt&eacute;s pour un entra&icirc;nement efficace &agrave; domicile.</p>
        <div class="meta">13 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/guides/comprendre-rpe-intensite/" class="guide-card">
      <div class="card-image img-placeholder">Photo RPE</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Technique</span>
        <h2>Comprendre le RPE et l'intensit&eacute;</h2>
        <p>&Eacute;chelle RPE, RIR et pourcentage de 1RM : comment doser l'intensit&eacute; pour optimiser chaque s&eacute;ance.</p>
        <div class="meta">9 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>Passez &agrave; la pratique</h2>
    <p>T&eacute;l&eacute;chargez AIVancePro et laissez le coach IA appliquer ces principes &agrave; votre entra&icirc;nement.</p>
    <a href="https://apps.apple.com/fr/app/aivancepro/id6756116760" class="btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">T&eacute;l&eacute;charger gratuitement</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
